
# https://jasonstitt.com/gitignore-whitelisting-patterns
# Ignore everything
*
# But descend into directories
!*/
# Recursively allow files under subtree
!/code/*.R
!/code/*.Rmd
!/code/*.rmd
# You can be specific with these rules
!.gitignore
!*.md
!*.Rmd
!*.rmd
.Rproj.user
.Rhistory
.RData
.Ruserdata
